title: Bernie Sanders Calls Out Hillary Clinton For Being Naive On Wall Street
text: Senator Bernie Sanders (I-Vt.) slammed Hillary Clinton as naive on Wall Street during the CNN Democratic debate on Tuesday night in Las Vegas. Sanders went on the attack as Hillary Clinton defended her stance on Wall Street regulatory policies during her time as a senator in New York. The former secretary of state stated that...
